---
import Pre from '@/components/pre.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { getCloudinaryImage } from '@/lib/utils'

let imgUrl = getCloudinaryImage('rimzzlabs/school-computer-laboratory')
let imgCaption = "A photo of computer desktop from my high school's computer laboratory"
---

<section class='flex flex-col lg:h-screen lg:flex-row items-center w-11/12 py-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl'>
  <figure class='max-lg:w-full'>
    <Image
      width={512}
      height={480}
      loading='lazy'
      decoding='async'
      class='lg:mr-auto h-80 w-full lg:w-96 md:h-auto object-cover rounded'
      src={imgUrl}
      alt={imgCaption}
      title={imgCaption}
    />
    <figcaption class='text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 pt-2'>
      <em>{imgCaption}</em>
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <div class='w-full pt-6 sm:pt-8 lg:pt-0 lg:pl-40'>
    <h2 class='text-4xl pb-6 md:pb-8 font-bold 2xl:text-5xl'>Journey - Part 1</h2>

    <div class='max-w-2xl text-neutral-100 space-y-4 md:space-y-6'>
      <Pre>Now we talking about my journey for which I became today.</Pre>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        When I was a kid, I have dream to become a pilot, but things started to change when my
        father gave me a smartphone. I discovered my true dream.
      </p>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        After receiving my first smarthphone, I always wondered how the thing was made, -how is it
        possible that we can connect with people far from us. I was just a kid with curiosity back
        then.
      </p>

      <div class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        It turns out, because of lack of tools and money, I never reach the point where I can study
        and experiment with the hardware.
      </div>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        So I just started over and started to learn programming, I was learning Java back then,
        which was also one of the courses of my class at my High School. It was awesome experience.
      </p>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        She teaches me about basic programming like, loop, condition, class, function, even OOP.
      </p>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        Fun fact, most of the female teachers are <em>&quot;fine&quot;</em> if you know what I mean.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
